    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Works made from the inner bark of the lime or linden, which is cut into strips and coarsely plaited. Examples include costume and decorations. The term is also applied to works made of similar flexible fibrous barks or similar materials.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
